{"type": "article", "id": 22305, "title": "10名漫画家玩接龙，日本交通卡就有了10幅海报", "description": "大触的世界好有趣。", "date": "2016-02-16T10:00:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 23421, "name": "交通卡"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 23422, "name": "漫画接龙"}, {"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 23423, "name": "PiTaPa"}], "category": 18, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150157AyEbi4wQ2XztCNUo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>日本 JR 发行的西瓜卡很多人都知道，但实际上日本的铁路错综复杂，私营铁路众多，不同地区都有自家主打的线路和通行的交通卡，由于各个发卡组织在不同的商家都有差异化的便利服务，因此像关西地区通行的 PiTaPa 卡也有自己的粉丝。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150150yhswWICAHYKO3EDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>微博用户@顽固的白煮蛋 就表示：“在关西一张 PiTaPa 就能彻底忘记 JR 的存在。”虽然不支持 7-11 和罗森，但是能在食堂刷超方便。</p>\n<p>最近，PiTaPa 为了推广自家的 IC 卡，找来 10 名漫画家搞了一场<a href=\"http://www.pitapa.com/kioku/\">「记忆漫画接龙」</a>。玩法是这样的，先给第一位漫画家展示一张 PiTaPa 广告画，漫画家观看 1 分钟后，自行临摹创作，下一名漫画家就照着上一人的作品临摹，以此类推，每个人的记忆时间只有一分钟，相当于漫画版的拷贝不走样。 </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=q0184yxvwko&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; min-height: 240px;\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150150zROTQkIntdewbhL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是原图，中间是 PiTaPa 的新吉祥物 ぴたまる</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150151X0kqRmipQFxa8PUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">山根庆丈，虽然画风像是北条司，但其实是个 90 后</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150151FYWyqBHILK1kEoxi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78431373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">山根庆丈的作品</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150152iNyOcoTgksqA68fb.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.37727273\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150152pbJHA5YGniPLuhZQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150152SysaoWTIfXiZDA96.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78431373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150153Za0yf4rMYQd16Wnq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">せきやゆりえ<b>，</b>东京的插画师，擅长绘制夸张激萌的少女和猫咪。</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150153YOihswtNJS47Qn8L.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">藤井亮，日本电通广告的插画师</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150154XcMgSUdoNyxbkh1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">スージー甘金</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150154uNbJdtEMxLWgG9Ke.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">フカヒレ</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061501555SQxUVKaYT6Zmn4G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">森田真法，代表作有《学园无赖》，《热血教师》</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150155GlKfFOpPcgS6wdbo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">しりあがり寿</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061501564I6fGWdYKnUyl9Fk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">寺田克也，游戏人设，同时也是《大猿王》的作者</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150156Vy62nS3qhaAtXTbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66384778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>100% ORANGE ，绘本作者</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">可以看到临摹到最后一人，基本上已经完全看不到原图的影子，而且最初的构图也被山根庆丈的忍者给带跑偏了……不过对 PiTaPa 来说要的就是这个效果，每张海报都是极佳的广告素材。</p>\n<p class=\"\">既然广告做得那么有趣，那么，下次去如果去关西旅游的话，不妨考虑尝试一下他家的 IC 卡。</p>\n\n\n\n"}